@startuml
title Datastream to Cloud Function Flow

start
:Datastream captures CDC event (in TMS database);
:Datastream writes event to Cloud Storage;

if (New File in Cloud Storage?) then (Yes)
    :Cloud Function (Cross-Dock Publisher) is Triggered;
    :Cloud Function requests TransportOrder from TMS Bridge (1-3 sec delay);
    if (TMS Bridge Responds?) then (Yes)
        :Process Data;
        :Publish to Downstream System (CALSuite ASB);
        end
    else (No)
        :Retry Processing;
        if (Max Retries Reached?) then (Yes)
            :Mark as Failed;
            end
        else (No)
            :Reattempt Processing;
        endif
    endif
else (No)
    :Wait for New Files;
endif

@enduml